OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers, a few perhaps heavy at first,
OL,7,Fwill fade away this evening to leave a
OL,8,Fdry night with often large amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud but also some clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FGenerally dry and fine, with
OL,12,Fjust a small chance of isolated
OL,13,Fthunderstorms developing. Temperatures
OL,14,Fclimbing, becoming very warm and humid
OL,15,Finland although onshore breezes will
OL,16,Fkeep coastal areas cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
